    • follow

      public ContainerLogs follow(boolean follow)
      Determines whether to stream log entries in real-time as they are generated by the container. Defaults to true.
      Parameters:
      follow - true to stream log entries in real-time as they are generated by the container, or false to return only the logs up to the current point in time without streaming new entries.

      this
